events.text: Welcome to your new league!
Marvin Williams retired.
The Nets traded a 2020 1st round pick (POR) to the Kings for a 2020 1st round pick (SAC).

The Wizards traded Bradley Beal to the Celtics for Vincent Poirier, Marcus Smart, Javonte Green, Romeo Langford, Tremont Waters, Semi Ojeleye, a 2020 1st round pick (MIN), a 2020 1st round pick (TOR), and a 2021 2nd round pick (BOS).
The Thunder traded Chris Paul to the Clippers for Mfiondu Kabengele, Terance Mann, JaMychal Green, Amir Coffey, Rodney McGruder, Johnathan Motley, Ivica Zubac, and Landry Shamet.
The Mavericks traded Tim Hardaway Jr. and Seth Curry to the Raptors for Kyle Lowry.
The Lakers traded Kostas Antetokounmpo, J.R. Smith, and Quinn Cook to the Bucks for Robin Lopez.

The Wizards traded Vincent Poirier, Jerome Robinson, Marcus Smart, and a 2021 2nd round pick (BOS) to the Trailblazers for Mario Hezonja, Jaylen Hoard, Gary Trent Jr., Trevor Ariza, Anfernee Simons, and a 2026 2nd round pick (POR).

The Celtics traded Robert Williams, Gordon Hayward, a 2020 1st round pick (LAL), a 2021 1st round pick (BOS), and a 2023 1st round pick (BOS) to the Mavericks for Kristaps Porziņģis and Jalen Brunson.

The Bucks traded Cameron Reynolds, Frank Mason III, Ersan İlyasova, Wesley Matthews, Quinn Cook, a 2020 1st round pick (PHI), and a 2023 2nd round pick (MIL) to the Mavericks for Maxi Kleber, Delon Wright, and a 2020 1st round pick (LAL).
The Pelicans traded J.J. Redick, Darius Miller, Nicolò Melli, and a 2020 2nd round pick (LAL) to the Thunder for Steven Adams.
The Magic traded Aaron Gordon to the Heat for Kendrick Nunn, Andre Iguodala, KZ Okpala, a 2020 1st round pick (SAS), and a 2022 2nd round pick (MIA).

The Mavericks traded Dwight Powell, Willie Cauley-Stein, Cameron Reynolds, Frank Mason III, Antonius Cleveland, Quinn Cook, a 2020 1st round pick (PHI), and a 2026 1st round pick (DAL) to the Magic for Evan Fournier.
The Heat traded Aaron Gordon, Duncan Robinson, and Chris Silva to the Trailblazers for Marcus Smart, Moses Brown, Zach Collins, a 2021 2nd round pick (BOS), and a 2022 2nd round pick (POR).
The Pacers traded Domantas Sabonis to the Hawks for Clint Capela, De'Andre Hunter, and a 2021 1st round pick (ATL).
The Jazz traded Rudy Gobert to the Hawks for Dewayne Dedmon, a 2020 1st round pick (GS), a 2021 2nd round pick (CLE), and a 2022 2nd round pick (CLE).
The Bucks traded George Hill, D.J. Wilson, a 2020 1st round pick (LAL), and a 2025 2nd round pick (IND) to the Spurs for Dejounte Murray.
The Pacers traded Victor Oladipo to the Hawks for Brandon Goodwin, Bruno Fernando, and John Collins.
The Heat traded Kyle Alexander, Kelly Olynyk, and Moses Brown to the Pacers for T.J. Warren.
The Kings traded Jabari Parker to the Trailblazers for Rodney Hood, Chris Silva, and a 2021 1st round pick (POR).
The Heat traded T.J. Warren to the Grizzlies for Justise Winslow.
The Kings traded Richaun Holmes to the Raptors for Patrick McCaw and a 2023 2nd round pick (TOR).
The Raptors traded Dewan Hernandez, Matt Thomas, Seth Curry, and a 2020 2nd round pick (MIL) to the Kings for Cory Joseph.
